Experiment 1.1

b)DDL COMMANDS- ALTER & DROP

1. Add a column ‘SSN’ at the first position in the table EMPLOYEE

alter table EMPLOYEE add ssn int first;
Query OK, 0 rows affected (0.60 sec)
Records: 0  Duplicates: 0  Warnings: 0

